Sometimes Action may be cost too much time, skipping action will be useful in some way.
I think it's not a cool implements, but it's effective. 
if there are any other more effective way to impelement the skip action interface, please notice me :)

Code to reproduce the issue.

```
    Color3B tintColorRed(  255, 0, 0   );
    Size shadowOffset(12.0, 12.0);

    FontDefinition shadowTextDef;
    shadowTextDef._fontSize = 10;
    shadowTextDef._fontName = std::string("Marker Felt");

    shadowTextDef._shadow._shadowEnabled = true;
    shadowTextDef._shadow._shadowOffset  = shadowOffset;
    shadowTextDef._shadow._shadowOpacity = 1.0;
    shadowTextDef._shadow._shadowBlur    = 1.0;
    shadowTextDef._fontFillColor   = tintColorRed;

    // shadow only label
    auto fontShadow = cocos2d::Label::create();
    fontShadow->setString("Shadow Only Red Text");
    fontShadow->setFontDefinition(shadowTextDef);

    fontShadow->setSystemFontSize(70);
```

Correct effect, the label should be very large in size 70.
But the label will be shown in size 10
